data.description: **Back on market NO fault of the Seller, Seller to give 5K in closing cost assistance with an accepted offer, if you use the sellers preferred lender buyer can get an additional 1K towards closing costs**Welcome to your dream home! This elegant 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence boasts 1539 sq ft of modern luxury. Built just a year ago, the open-concept living space is highlighted by a sleek kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Enjoy the convenience of a 2-car garage and the comfort of a master suite. This contemporary gem is perfect for both family living and entertaining. Experience style, convenience, and charm in every corner of this meticulously designed home! Centrally located all the military bases!
